Inheritance:
Allows a class(child/Derived) to acquire properties and behaviors of another class(parent/Base).
Type of inheritance in java oops.
1.Single inheritance
2.Multiple inheritance(through interfaces only)
3.Multilevel inheritance
4.Hierarchical Inheritance
5.Hybrid Inheritance (Combination)

Supported with classes : Single,Multilevel,Hierarchical
Not supported with classes : Multiple,Hybrid(but possible via interface)

Task:
